Section - Personamat
¶
¶Before entering the Personamat:
¶
	if the Personamat is closed, try opening the Personamat.
¶
¶The glowing purple crystal is a fixed in place device inside the 
Personamat.
¶
¶Before switching on the glowing purple crystal:
¶
	if the player is not inside the Personamat, try entering the 
Personamat;
¶
	if the Personamat is open, try closing the Personamat.
